      "category": "team",
      "content": "### Summary\nReflected Cross-Site Scripting attack on `mackeeperapp2.mackeeper.com`.\nThe problem in `/landings/land/1/ron_cleanprot17/index.php` script that take any GET parameter and pass value of this parameter directly to HTML code of the page.\n\n### Step to reproduce\n`http://mackeeperapp3.mackeeper.com/landings/land/3/ron_clean_17_app3_alerts/index.php?kola=bro\"></options></form><img src=x onerror=alert(document.domain)>`",
